TY  - JOUR
T1  - Models of New Product Diffusion Through Advertising and Word-of-Mouth
AU  - Dodson, Joe A.
AU  - Muller, Eitan
Y1  - 1978/11/01
PY  - 1978
DA  - 1978/11/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.24.15.1568
